Class PowerSkyHook

  • java.lang.Object
    • think.rpgitems.power.impl.BasePower
      • think.rpgitems.power.impl.PowerSkyHook
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Power, PowerBowShoot, PowerLeftClick, PowerPlain, PowerRightClick, PowerSneak, PowerSprint
    public class PowerSkyHook
extends BasePower
implements PowerRightClick, PowerLeftClick, PowerSneak, PowerSprint, PowerPlain, PowerBowShoot
    Power skyhook.

    The skyhook power will allow the user to hook on to material up to distance blocks away
